p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u00e2m ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian sinh ho\u1ea1t chung c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c, n\u00ean ngo\u00e0i m\u1eb7t th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 ra th\u00ec b\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ec7n nghi, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. M\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng khu b\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng theo c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ch\u1eef U, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed9i tr\u1ee3 di chuy\u1ec3n linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 thao t\u00e1c nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1046\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/16-PHONG-KHACH.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"938\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/16-PHONG-KHACH.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/16-PHONG-KHACH-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/16-PHONG-KHACH-768x480.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/16-PHONG-KHACH-1024x640.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\u0110i\u1ec1u th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u1edf ki\u1ec3u b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c n\u00e0y l\u00e0 khu qu\u1ea7y bar sang ch\u1ea3nh. M\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh nh\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u1ea5m c\u00fang.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u00f4i d\u00f9ng m\u00e0u ghi x\u00e1m l\u00e0m t\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o ph\u1ed1i kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u1edbi m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a t\u1ee7 b\u1ebfp tr\u00ean, t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng cho gian b\u1ebfp. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1044,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[154],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1043","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-chia-se-kien-thuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1043","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1043"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1043\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1044"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1043"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1043"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1043"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{